metadata.description: Free icon set to the world

name: neuicons
description: Neu is a crisp cohesive growing icon set library that provides wide range categories. Based on 24 pixel-perfect grid material, it will match with any of your app, website, design project. Created with a simple basic object, combine it with other shapes, and finish it with passion. You can use Neu icons for a personal and commercial purpose for free using CCBY 4.0 international attribution.
author: Royyan Wijaya <royyanwijaya@live.com> (neuicons.com)
